data.description: Escape to your own personal retreat, just moments from the BEACH! This isn’t your average RENOVATED townhouse—it’s a modern haven designed for relaxation and comfort. Really SPACIOUS rooms, flooded w/natural light, sunroom that beckons you to unwind with a good book or simply soak up the sunshine. With 2 master bedrooms upstairs, each w/private luxurious bathrooms, boasting high-end finishes & a contemporary vibe, this home offers the perfect blend of style & functionality. A half bath is conveniently located on the first floor. The end unit, a semi-detached house with plenty of space on the front, side,or backyard; tons of storage, & minimal maintenance. Enjoy your personal little paradise relaxing in a jacuzzi (conveys), or have friends over- there is space for everyone! Step outside to enjoy the view of nature and even have your own little garden. Schedule your showing today & discover the coastal lifestyle you’ve been dreaming of!  P.S. You MUST check the Main MasterBath First ;)
